","value":"[[6d6+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] damage and you or ally loses [[2d6]] hit points."},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"[[6d10+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] damage, and you or ally loses [[4d6]] hit points."},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"[[10d10+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] damage and you or ally loses [[6d6]] hit points."},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"[[2d8*10+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] damage and you or ally loses [[8d6]] hit points."},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>The spell now deals half damage on a miss.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>You or an ally now lose one less die of hit points (for example, 3d6 instead of 4d6).</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>The first time each battle you miss with this spell, if the escalation die is 3+, you can reroll the attack by having you or your ally lose the same amount of hit points again.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/skills/emerald_06.jpg","_id":"TePzdnY7Mceb8EhJ"}
{"name":"Touch of Wizardry","permission":{"default":0},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"Chaos Mage"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":""},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":""},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>You gain a random spell from the wizard class. Whenever you take a full heal-up, randomly choose a wizard spell of the highest level you can cast. For the rest of the day, you know this wizard spell and can cast it according to its normal usage pattern&mdash;at-will, cyclic, once per battle, recharge, or daily&mdash;when that option comes up during your chaos mage spellcasting sequence.</p><p>If the wizard spell refers to Intelligence, you can replace that ability score with references to Charisma.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>You gain a random wizard talent at the start of each day. Roll a [[d3]]. 1: Abjuration; 2: Evocation; 3: High Arcana (<em>counter magic</em>). Replace references to &ldquo;wizard&rdquo; in these talents with &ldquo;chaos mage&rdquo; and Intelligence with Charisma.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>You gain a single daily use of the wizard&rsquo;s <em>utility spell</em>, cast at your level or lower.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>If you don&rsquo;t like the first random wizard spell you select for the day, you can determine another random wizard spell. You&rsquo;re stuck with the second one.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/spells/light-blue-1.jpg","_id":"QDEsRAz1icP8ighL"}
{"name":"Trace of Corruption","permission":{"default":0},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"Chaos Mage"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged spell"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"You or one nearby ally; the target must have a positive or conflicted relationship with a villainous icon"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>The target rolls a save against each save ends effect affecting it. Then the target can heal using a recovery from a nearby ally (target&rsquo;s choice, even if that ally isn&rsquo;t willing).</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/spells/evil-eye-eerie-1.jpg","_id":"vH98UdNEZfTwEvM2"}
{"name":"Trace of the Divine","permission":{"default":0},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"Chaos Mage"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":""},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":""},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>You gain a random spell from the cleric class. Whenever you take a full heal-up, randomly choose a cleric spell of the highest level you can cast. For the rest of the day, you know this cleric spell and can cast it according to its normal usage pattern—at-will, once per battle, recharge, or daily—when that option comes up during your chaos mage spellcasting sequence.</p><p>If the cleric spell refers to Wisdom, you can replace that ability score with references to Charisma.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>At the start of the day, choose a random cleric invocation, excepting those from the healing domain. You can use that invocation as if you were a cleric once this day as a quick action.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>While you have an <em>air </em>or<em> water </em>warp effect active, when you heal using a recovery or cast a spell that lets an ally heal using a recovery, add an extra recovery die to the healing.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>In addition to the random invocation you gain at the start of the day, you also get the talent/domain powers that go with it.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/spells/protect-sky-1.jpg","_id":"1mQwfHb1xehu971o"}
{"name":"Twisted Beam","permission":{"default":0},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"Chaos Mage"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"at-will"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged spell"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"One nearby enemy"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":"[[d20+@cha.mod+@std+@atk.a.bonus]] vs. PD"},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":"[[1d6+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] fire damage."},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":"Lightning damage equal to half the damage from a natural even hit, and you can roll another twisted beam attack against an enemy you haven’t targeted with it this turn."},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":"[[3]] ongoing acid damage."},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":"[[3d6+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] damage , [[6]] ongoing damage."},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"[[5d6+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] damage, [[9]] ongoing damage."},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"[[7d8+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] damage, [[12]] ongoing damage."},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"[[9d8+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] damage, [[18]] ongoing damage."},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>This spell can now target far away enemies.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>A natural odd miss now deals half natural even hit damage.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>The first save against the ongoing damage from a natural even miss is a hard save (16+). The second and subsequent saves are normal.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/spells/beam-eerie-2.jpg","_id":"8qlagPcERqKYlw94"}
{"name":"Unsummoning","permission":{"default":0},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"Chaos Mage"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":7},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged Spell"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"One nearby non-undead enemy that the GM hasn’t given a proper name, or that doesn’t play a key role in the current storyline"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":"[[d20+@cha.mod+@std+@atk.a.bonus]] vs. MD"},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":"The target is sent elsewhere, possibly to a location that’s close enough for the PCs to have to deal with it in a subsequent battle. It might also go somewhere “interesting.”  See Effect."},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":"[[7d10+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] psychic damage."},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>Replace the target with the GM&rsquo;s choice of an undamaged and hostile undead creature that is one level lower than the original target. If the target was a large or double-strength creature, the replacement must be large or double-strength, or perhaps two normal undead instead of one show up. Ditto for huge/triple-strength targets. Therefore you&rsquo;re only slightly reducing the raw power of the opposition; the advantage of using the spell is that you&rsquo;re getting rid of an enemy you match up badly against and dropping the level of the opposition by one. The disadvantage, of course, is that you&rsquo;ll probably have to face that enemy again.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"On miss: [[8d10+@cha.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] psychic damage."},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>This spell can now also target an entire mob of mooks. If the attack hits, replace them with a mob of undead mooks that is one level lower.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>You don&rsquo;t expend the spell when you miss with it.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/spells/wind-grasp-eerie-3.jpg","_id":"rPKT1ojBOAZekdoD"}
{"name":"War Drums","permission":{"default":0},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"Chaos Mage"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"at-will"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged Spell"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>The next natural odd attack roll you or one of your allies makes this battle that hits an enemy deals [[13+@atk.a.bonus]] extra damage.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":"[[23+@atk.a.bonus]] extra damage."},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"[[33+@atk.a.bonus]] extra damage."},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"[[53+@atk.a.bonus]] extra damage."},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"[[83+@atk.a.bonus]] extra damage."},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>Add [[@cha.dmg]] to the extra damage.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>When you cast this spell, each nearby enemy that&rsquo;s staggered also takes [[2d6]] thunder damage ([[4d6]] thunder damage at 8th level).</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>When this spell&rsquo;s effect deals the extra damage, you can roll a hard save (16+). If you succeed, the <em>war drums</em> keep beating and the effect extends to the next natural odd hit this battle! (And so on if you keep succeeding.)</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/spells/enchant-jade-3.jpg","_id":"jL23i0FCRbewhu2G"}
{"name":"Warped Healing","permission":{"default":0},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"Chaos Mage"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"once-per-battle"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Close-Quarters Spell"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"Two nearby allies, or you and one nearby ally"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>Randomly choose one of the targets. That target can heal using a recovery. The other target gains [[10]] temporary hit points and grows a strange eye, limb, or other physical feature that lasts as long as the temporary hit points do.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":"[[20]] temporary hit points."},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"[[30]] temporary hit points."},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"[[45]] temporary hit points."},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"[[70]] temporary hit points."},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/skills/shadow_18.jpg","_id":"ZoiHc8zi8Ll5pwCZ"}
{"name":"Whiff of Sorcery","permission":{"default":0},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"Chaos Mage"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":""},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":""},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>You gain a random spell from the sorcerer class. Whenever you take a full heal-up, randomly choose a sorcerer spell of the highest level you can cast. For the rest of the day, you know this sorcerer spell and can cast it according to its normal usage pattern&mdash;at-will, once per battle, recharge, or daily&mdash;when that option comes up during your chaos mage spellcasting sequence.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>Twice per day, you can gather power as if you were a sorcerer in order to deal double damage with either a sorcerer spell or a chaos mage spell the next time you cast a spell. You also gain the chaotic benefit for gathering power. (Note that you should have already determined the type of spell you will be casting, since you select a spell type when you roll initiative and at the end of each turn, so you&rsquo;re generally better off waiting to gather power when you know you have an attack or iconic spell coming.)</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>While you have an <em>air</em> or <em>fire </em>warp effect active, add [[@cha.dmg]] fire damage to your miss damage.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>If you don&rsquo;t like the first random sorcerer spell you select for the day, you can determine another random sorcerer spell. You&rsquo;re stuck with the second one.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/spells/fog-blue-1.jpg","_id":"OL19T59KVDkhKVPb"}
{"name":"Yours!","permission":{"default":0},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerSourceName":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"Chaos Mage"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"at-will"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged Spell"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"You or one ally in the battle, chosen randomly"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p><em>Roll a d20&nbsp; [[1d20]]</em></p><p><em>1&ndash;10</em>: The target can heal using a recovery.</p><p><em>11&ndash;20</em>: The target can make a basic attack as a free action.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":null},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>When this spell allows a target to attack, the attack deals half damage on a miss instead of normal miss damage</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>The target can move as a free action before using a recovery or attacking.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>When the target heals using a recovery, it adds hit points equal to [[d10*@ed]] to that healing.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/skills/shadow_10.jpg","_id":"wojN5keXOyuzSqBG"}
